questions.quote: Okay, I've had it with the hair jokes. Tomorrow morning, before we leave, I'm going to the salon.
I like this one. It seems to say, "I love you and that's why I have to kill you."
Happy Holidays. Feliz Navidad. Allo, and Merry Christmas. Ohh thank you sir. Here's some joy.
We can't leave now! There was this one baby, Haley, who was favourite to win and she got croup, so she had to stay home! This competition just blew wide open, folks!
Really? Okay, so why don't you tell me what happened to Ross Junior year at Disneyland?
Don't worry, I'll be back before you know it. Yes it will be the same. Because I know, that's how. I promise.
No, hey, I get that, okay, I get that big time. And I'm happy for ya, but I'm tired of having a relationship with your answering machine! Okay, I don't know what to do anymore.
Oh, did the little rich boy have a problem with the butler? Yes, mine's worse!
Yeah, once again, I am sorry. Thank you. Bye. I just had to turn down a job catering a funeral for sixty people.
Oh, I wish he was a doll, then I could get a Rachel doll and bump them together and make kissy noises. Oh! And he has the most beautiful name, I never realised it, Joshua! Josh-u-a! Joshua! Josh.
